      "sc:description": "NeuroML is a model description language for computational neuroscience that enables the creation, visualization, validation, and simulation of standardized models of neural systems. The NeuroML ecosystem comprises a language specification, libraries, and software tools to facilitate interoperability and promote open, transparent, and reproducible science.",
